{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/my-first-article/redis2/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"Redis","caption":"Photo by <u><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/Nc5Q_CEcY44\">Redis</a></u>","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/ca4aa/redis_img.png","srcSet":"/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/77001/redis_img.png 75w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/4ec1c/redis_img.png 150w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/ca4aa/redis_img.png 300w","sizes":"(min-width: 300px) 300px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/dd377/redis_img.webp 75w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/40ac4/redis_img.webp 150w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/9e761/redis_img.webp 300w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 300px) 300px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":400.40000000000003}}}},"body":"<h2>Redis 설치하기</h2>\n<p>Redis를 window방법이나 Mac에서 brew로 이용해서 설치하는 방법들이 있지만 어디에서 설치방법이 동일한 docker로 설치하는 방벙으로 진행을 해볼까 한다. docker에 대해서 어느정도 알고 docker가 설치 되어있다는 가정하에 설명을 해보겠다.</p>\n<h3>docker-compose.yml</h3>\n<p>docker로 특정 프로그램을 설치할때는 버전을 써주는게 제일 좋다. 그렇지만 지금은 학습을 위한 것이므로 lastest버전으로 사용을 해보겠다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">services:\n  redis-stack:\n    image: redis/redis-stack\n    container_name: redis-stack-compose\n    restart: always\n    command: [\"redis-server\", \"--requirepass\", \"systempass\"]\n    ports:\n      - 6379:6379\n      - 8001:8001</code></pre></div>\n<p>여기서 자세하게 볼 부분은 image와 command쪽이다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>redis/redis-stack는 redis/redis-stack-server에 Redis Insight가 추가된 이미지이다. Redis Insight를 같이 사용할려고 하기 때문에 선택을 해주었다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>redis의 기본 아이디는 <code class=\"language-text\">default</code>이며 비밀번호는 <code class=\"language-text\">systempass</code>이며 만약 비밀번호를 변경하고 싶다면 이부분을 수정하면 된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>docker compose up</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker compose up -d</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>redis의 컨테이너가 정상적으로 실행 되었는지 확인</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker ps</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Intellij IDEA UE에서 연결해보기</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Database 탭 클릭하기</li>\n</ol>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.63636363636364%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/c9b55/redis-ue-1.webp 165w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/f2908/redis-ue-1.webp 330w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/cc661/redis-ue-1.webp 660w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/a66df/redis-ue-1.webp 990w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/d33d4/redis-ue-1.webp 1320w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/d802c/redis-ue-1.webp 1399w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/04c57/redis-ue-1.png 165w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/d9ecf/redis-ue-1.png 330w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/1f083/redis-ue-1.png 660w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/7a3d6/redis-ue-1.png 990w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/78958/redis-ue-1.png 1320w,\n/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/01ccc/redis-ue-1.png 1399w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c9276a30f683aaaa436ff6bbb7c81456/1f083/redis-ue-1.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Intellij IDEA UE\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Intellij IDEA UE</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Data Source > \"Redis\"검색하고 클릭하기</li>\n</ol>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/27156a15911f676d614082102c65f4ca/c9b55/redis-ue-2.webp 165w,\n/static/27156a15911f676d614082102c65f4ca/f2908/redis-ue-2.webp 330w,\n/static/27156a15911f676d614082102c65f4ca/cc661/redis-ue-2.webp 660w,\n/static/27156a15911f676d614082102c65f4ca/415aa/redis-ue-2.webp 867w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/27156a15911f676d614082102c65f4ca/04c57/redis-ue-2.png 165w,\n/static/27156a15911f676d614082102c65f4ca/d9ecf/redis-ue-2.png 330w,\n/static/27156a15911f676d614082102c65f4ca/1f083/redis-ue-2.png 660w,\n/static/27156a15911f676d614082102c65f4ca/264eb/redis-ue-2.png 867w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/27156a15911f676d614082102c65f4ca/1f083/redis-ue-2.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Intellij IDEA UE\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Intellij IDEA UE</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Host : localhost / port : 6379 / User : default / Password : systempass 입력 후 연결하기</li>\n</ol>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c5ba993172cc50d06b61c48514044ffe/c9b55/redis-ue-3.webp 165w,\n/static/c5ba993172cc50d06b61c48514044ffe/f2908/redis-ue-3.webp 330w,\n/static/c5ba993172cc50d06b61c48514044ffe/cc661/redis-ue-3.webp 660w,\n/static/c5ba993172cc50d06b61c48514044ffe/b116a/redis-ue-3.webp 912w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c5ba993172cc50d06b61c48514044ffe/04c57/redis-ue-3.png 165w,\n/static/c5ba993172cc50d06b61c48514044ffe/d9ecf/redis-ue-3.png 330w,\n/static/c5ba993172cc50d06b61c48514044ffe/1f083/redis-ue-3.png 660w,\n/static/c5ba993172cc50d06b61c48514044ffe/8b69f/redis-ue-3.png 912w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c5ba993172cc50d06b61c48514044ffe/1f083/redis-ue-3.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Intellij IDEA UE\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Intellij IDEA UE</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>이제 console창에서 명령어로 데이터 조회,삽입등 수행하면 된다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.63636363636364%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/c9b55/redis-ue-4.webp 165w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/f2908/redis-ue-4.webp 330w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/cc661/redis-ue-4.webp 660w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/a66df/redis-ue-4.webp 990w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/d33d4/redis-ue-4.webp 1320w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/d802c/redis-ue-4.webp 1399w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/04c57/redis-ue-4.png 165w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/d9ecf/redis-ue-4.png 330w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/1f083/redis-ue-4.png 660w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/7a3d6/redis-ue-4.png 990w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/78958/redis-ue-4.png 1320w,\n/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/01ccc/redis-ue-4.png 1399w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f39a1410c5bbb0adede00c4cf2739162/1f083/redis-ue-4.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Intellij IDEA UE\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Intellij IDEA UE</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>Docker로 Redis Insight 설치하기</h2>\n<p>만약, Docker로 Redis를 설치하는 과정에서 redis/redis-stack을 선택했을 경우 Redis Insight가 함께 설치되며, 8001 포트를 publish(-p 옵션)하면 접속할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>지금은 그게 아니고 Redis Insight를 따로 도커 컨테이너로 띄웠을때를 알아보자</p>\n<p>redisinsight 이미지를 그냥 빌드를 하고 실행해서 기존 redis와 연결을 할려고 하면 연결이 되지 않는걸 알수가 있다. 그 이유는 docker의 네트워크 설정을 안해줬기 때문이다.</p>\n<h3>네트워크 설정</h3>\n<p>네트워크 설정은 생각보다 간단하다. 우선 네트워크를 redis_network이름으로 하나 생성한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">docker network create redis_network</code></pre></div>\n<p>다음과 출력 값을 보게 되면 ip주소가 하나 있는데 이걸 나중에 redis insight쪽에 localhost 대신 적어 주면 연결이 된다.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.06060606060606%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/342ccc006337ad2c86b0ebb4664f2889/c9b55/docker-network-2.webp 165w,\n/static/342ccc006337ad2c86b0ebb4664f2889/f2908/docker-network-2.webp 330w,\n/static/342ccc006337ad2c86b0ebb4664f2889/cc661/docker-network-2.webp 660w,\n/static/342ccc006337ad2c86b0ebb4664f2889/a1ca4/docker-network-2.webp 875w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/342ccc006337ad2c86b0ebb4664f2889/04c57/docker-network-2.png 165w,\n/static/342ccc006337ad2c86b0ebb4664f2889/d9ecf/docker-network-2.png 330w,\n/static/342ccc006337ad2c86b0ebb4664f2889/1f083/docker-network-2.png 660w,\n/static/342ccc006337ad2c86b0ebb4664f2889/71c8e/docker-network-2.png 875w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/342ccc006337ad2c86b0ebb4664f2889/1f083/docker-network-2.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"redis_network\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>redis_network</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>수정된 docker compose.yml</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">services:\n  redis-stack:\n    image: redis/redis-stack\n    container_name: redis-stack-compose\n    restart: always\n    command: [\"redis-server\", \"--requirepass\", \"systempass\"]\n    ports:\n      - 6379:6379\n      - 8001:8001\n    networks:\n      - redis_network\n\n  redisinsight:\n    image: redis/redisinsight:latest\n    container_name: redisinsight\n    ports:\n      - 5540:5540\n    volumes:\n      - redisinsight:/data\n    networks:\n      - redis_network\n\nvolumes:\n  redisinsight:\n\nnetworks:\n  redis_network:</code></pre></div>\n<p>redis-stack쪽이랑 redisinsight쪽에 networks를 추가 해주고 아래쪽에도 추가적으로 적어 주었다. 추후에 docker compose up을 하게 되면 두개의 컨테이너가 연결된걸 확인 할 수가 있다.</p>\n<p>전에 띄웠던 redis를 삭제해주고 다시 docker compose up을 해준뒤 <a href=\"http://localhost:5540/%EC%97%90\">http://localhost:5540/에</a> 접속을 해준다.</p>\n<p>위에서도 한번 언급하였는데 기존에 localhost가 적혀 있던 자리에 아까 확인했던 ip주소를 입력하면 된다.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/c9b55/redis-view.webp 165w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/f2908/redis-view.webp 330w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/cc661/redis-view.webp 660w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/a66df/redis-view.webp 990w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/d33d4/redis-view.webp 1320w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/9a996/redis-view.webp 1378w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/04c57/redis-view.png 165w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/d9ecf/redis-view.png 330w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/1f083/redis-view.png 660w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/7a3d6/redis-view.png 990w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/78958/redis-view.png 1320w,\n/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/e40ed/redis-view.png 1378w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/1917945e96826c2c7692a056a87ae6a5/1f083/redis-view.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"http://localhost:5540/\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p><a href=\"http://localhost:5540/\">http://localhost:5540/</a></p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>","categories":["Redis","Docker"],"date":"August 05, 2024","description":"Redis","id":"c7216bc4-9906-5ed2-b760-f19edc9f7891","keywords":["Redis","단기 심화 부트캠프","Sparta"],"slug":"/my-first-article/redis2/","title":"[Redis] Redis Docker로 설치하기","readingTime":{"text":"5 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}